milestones.description: Allan Border and Wessels's 140-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 112 between Graham Yallop and David Hookes
This is the highest match aggregate (494) involving teams Australia & Pakistan in ODIs
Imran Khan has broken the record for most ODIs (16) as captain for PAK, going past Javed Miandad
